{"tid":2339462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最後淨土失守 南極洲58人確診","createTime":"2020-12-24T15:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T16:10:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76238e0b17261002b545b7bda210bfcd1d6e311f","tid":2339462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/KHT5XVFJ5BDF7HTZHBX3KLXZ6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2FKHT5XVFJ5BDF7HTZHBX3KLXZ6Q%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=2997fb00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2FKHT5XVFJ5BDF7HTZHBX3KLXZ6Q%2F&h=54130722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/KHT5XVFJ5BDF7HTZHBX3KLXZ6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n最後淨土失守 南極洲58人確診<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FVDsAcyeBS6a_YTopDQoVHP6-V4=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SK7AGE3JTVDV3F2JC2DOTR5XBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFVDsAcyeBS6a_YTopDQoVHP6-V4%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSK7AGE3JTVDV3F2JC2DOTR5XBE.jpg&h=f68a0937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■智利在南極洲設立的軍事基地有人確診武漢肺炎。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎殺入南極洲，攻陷最後淨土。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英法有限度通關  3,000司機恐邊境度聖誕<br />\n意大利現變種個案<br />\n<br />\n智利軍方周一宣佈南極洲最北端軍事基地有36人確診；翌日衞生當局指海軍的一艘物資船有21人染疫，另外一宗個案出現在一個空軍基地的平民工作人員所住的村落，該染疫的物資船曾停泊在這村落。軍方指首批染疫36人中有26人是軍人，十人是維修合約商的平民僱員，未有人出現併發症，所有人正接受隔離檢疫。物資船有三名船員上周確診，全船208人正在船上隔離。據稱該船曾在上月27日至本月10日期間到南極洲特里尼蒂半島的基地服務。<br />\n<br />\n另外，世衞指周日的一周確診數字破新高，比上一周新增6%，即460萬宗，死亡人數新增4%，即7.9萬宗。美國新增160萬宗個案，一周增幅為14%，累計個案仍是全球最多。歐洲染疫死亡人數突破50萬大關，過去一周新增逾3.6萬人，佔全球總數一半。<br />\n<br />\n英國因出現的武肺變種病毒被多國封關。繼丹麥和法國發現變種病毒株後，意大利周日亦發現一宗感染變種病毒個案。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"e8dacdc436c2e438e87f1ebc82b30ca1700d4c01","tid":2339462,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4cd1f75d81124b313a70bf47322d9675e26c41","tid":2339462,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"仲有北極守得住"},{"pid":"1328e789c202ec488eb09e34d3e95049ea7c4929","tid":2339462,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4cd1f75d81124b313a70bf47322d9675e26c41","tid":2339462,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"仲有北極守得住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"北極撚有地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae42112b47234b37aef63130f4e42530ea263ee2","tid":2339462,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"人類真係地球病毒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148b0de5e36bb96bbceaae4a5f018e4bc85f741e","tid":2339462,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1328e789c202ec488eb09e34d3e95049ea7c4929","tid":2339462,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4cd1f75d81124b313a70bf47322d9675e26c41","tid":2339462,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"仲有北極守得住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"北極撚有地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"係唔係最後都係土地問題 而唔關病毒事"},{"pid":"3c3926ac429088d7a0339ace20a9e45295538785","tid":2339462,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"148b0de5e36bb96bbceaae4a5f018e4bc85f741e","tid":2339462,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1328e789c202ec488eb09e34d3e95049ea7c4929","tid":2339462,"uid":196924,"li